      "title": "Saman Ekanayake appointed Secretary to President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Saman Ekanayake has been appointed as the Secretary to the President.",
        "The appointment was made by the newly-elected President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Ekanayake previously served as the Secretary to the Prime Minister when Ranil Wickremesinghe was serving in that position."
